(laughing)
Oh, what a weird movie.

00:22.623 --> 00:24.957
I know.
Vin Diesel always looks like

00:24.959 --> 00:27.526
he can't decide
what he's smelling.

00:28.962 --> 00:30.195
He's, like...

00:30.197 --> 00:32.331
Gasoline...?

00:32.333 --> 00:33.832
(sniffs)

00:33.834 --> 00:35.634
No.

00:35.636 --> 00:37.469
It's cake.

00:37.471 --> 00:39.538
Come here.

00:40.807 --> 00:42.708
(chuckles)

00:46.312 --> 00:48.414
Pretend I no here.

00:49.382 --> 00:51.016
Edna...

00:51.018 --> 00:52.718
it's okay,
you-you can go.

00:52.720 --> 00:54.486
Okay. Thank you, Mr. Eli.

00:54.488 --> 00:55.387
Thank you.

01:00.527 --> 01:02.194
Wha... E-Edna, wha...

01:02.196 --> 01:04.663
what are you doing?

01:04.665 --> 01:07.933
Tomorrow I work from home.

01:09.169 --> 01:11.236
Where were we?

01:12.338 --> 01:14.540
Eli, there's something
you should know.

01:14.542 --> 01:15.908
Uh, okay.

01:15.910 --> 01:18.343
Do you want to see
if I can guess?

01:18.345 --> 01:20.045
Maybe we both say it
at the same time.

01:20.047 --> 01:22.014
Okay, one, two...

01:22.016 --> 01:23.348
You're bisexual.
I have a son.

01:23.350 --> 01:25.184
You have a son.

01:25.186 --> 01:26.919
Yeah.

01:28.221 --> 01:30.856
If-if you want to break up,
I understand.

01:30.858 --> 01:32.591
No, no. Are you kidding?

01:32.593 --> 01:33.892
I-I love kids.

01:33.894 --> 01:38.097
Why, I would rent a baby
six times a year...

01:38.099 --> 01:40.699
if that were legal.

01:40.701 --> 01:42.201
Well, Gene is 12.

01:42.203 --> 01:45.204
Well, you know what, Elsa?
I like you.

01:45.206 --> 01:47.106
So I'm still in.

01:47.108 --> 01:48.874
(chuckles)

01:48.876 --> 01:51.276
Eli.

01:51.278 --> 01:54.213
You have company?
Yes.

01:54.215 --> 01:56.415
Is it girl company?

01:56.417 --> 01:58.383
Yes.

01:58.385 --> 02:01.153
Does she by any chance
have any Q-tips?

02:02.922 --> 02:05.224
I guess I have
to tell you...

02:05.226 --> 02:07.993
I have a dad.

02:09.929 --> 02:14.099
¶ Daddy took me to the zoo

02:14.101 --> 02:15.934
¶ <i>Na, na, na, na</i> ¶

